    "is_free": false,
    "description": "《秘典》是一款节奏快、充满动作的第一人称射击游戏，设定在一个由海盗和超自然生物居住的世界，游戏玩法灵感来自于最新的高强度动作游戏。根据《秘典》的描述，玩家可以将魔法与复古科技结合，打造强大的武器。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/2a5ff3e08a2f0626ed111a59c42b2d8a.avif?t=1735809311\" width=640 height=66 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗与探索</strong></h2>参与快速激烈的战斗，释放你最强的武器库，在疯狂的竞技场战斗和探索之间无缝切换。搜寻环境的每一个角落，发现制作和升级武器所需的重要资源。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/a395c4b68201566059ab9cce98115cd4.poster.avif?t=1735809311\" width=620 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/a395c4b68201566059ab9cce98115cd4.webm?t=1735809311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武器制作</strong></h2>在《秘典》中，你获得了一本神秘的手稿，里面记录了制作来自不同时代的强大武器的说明。这些武器的全部力量将是你在这个超自然的海盗世界中前进的必要条件。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/bd2bae6b49448df24e0701642f303788.poster.avif?t=1735809311\" width=620 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/bd2bae6b49448df24e0701642f303788.webm?t=1735809311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>手雷</strong></h2>在你最喜欢的火器和可靠的手雷之间交替使用。手雷既可以作为支持武器，增强火器伤害，也可以作为战斗循环的辅助。许多升级武器都利用了手雷效果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/0d2d7bb94aa19be4c16d8beeeedbd77b.poster.avif?t=1735809311\" width=620 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/0d2d7bb94aa19be4c16d8beeeedbd77b.webm?t=1735809311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269000/extras/0504dfdf83d65556f15bfb9b9ceb5117.avif?t=1735809311\" width=640 height=94 /></span>",
